// Alert
// Status alert banner with type-specific icon and optional dismiss button.
// Supports success, warning, error, and info variants.

FUNCTION getAlertStyles(type) -> string
  Returns Tailwind color classes (background, border, text) for the given alert type.

---

FUNCTION getAlertIcon(type) -> ReactNode
  Returns the appropriate SVG icon for the alert type (checkmark, warning triangle, X circle, info).

---

FUNCTION handleDismiss()
  Calls the onDismiss callback.
  Hides the alert by clearing its visible state.

---

FUNCTION Alert(props) -> ReactNode                                        EXPORT
  Renders an alert banner with an icon, title, optional message body, and optional dismiss button.
  Applies type-specific color styling via getAlertStyles.
  IF dismissible, shows a close button that calls handleDismiss.
  Returns null if the alert has been dismissed.
